kpi_info.title: The longest call setup time for subscriber failure released connections
kpi_info.use: The longest call setup time in the report period for subscriber failure released connections. Clear code range for internal failure released connection: C00...FFF. The unit of time in ASCII report is seconds, in XML reports it is 10 milliseconds.
